item.title: CVE-2020-7864|2024-08-04T09:41:01.955Z -- raonwiz -- dext5editor
item.description: Parameter manipulation can bypass authentication to cause file upload and execution. This will execute the remote code. This issue affects: Raonwiz DEXT5Editor versions prior to 3.5.1405747.1100.03.
